<ab><expan>L<ex>ieben</ex></expan>
<expan>fr<ex>eunde</ex></expan>, als ir uns
                            <expan>verschr<ex>iben</ex></expan> habt von unsers
                            <expan>h<ex>er</ex>ren</expan> graf <expan>Joh<ex>an</ex></expan> von
                        Wertheim sache <expan>weg<ex>en</ex></expan> etc., das
                            <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> wir wol <expan>vernom<ex>en</ex></expan>.
                        Nu als ir in <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>m</expan>
<expan>nehst<ex>en</ex></expan> brief wol
                            <expan>v<ex>er</ex>nom<ex>m</ex>en</expan> habt, wie
                                <expan>desselb<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
<expan>uns<ex>er</ex>s</expan>
<expan>h<ex>er</ex>ren</expan> von Wertheim capplan
                            <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>m</expan>
<expan>b<ex>urger</ex></expan> und <expan>ratgeselle<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>Sigmund<ex>en</ex></expan>
<expan>Strom<ex>er</ex></expan> den tag widerbot, der hat auf die zeit von
                        keins <expan>and<ex>er</ex>n</expan> tags <expan>weg<ex>en</ex></expan> niht
                                <expan>geworbe<ex>n</ex></expan>. Wie
                        <expan>daru<ex>m</ex>b</expan>, so <expan>well<ex>e</ex>n</expan> wir umb
                                <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan>
<expan>will<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
<expan>dems<ex>elben</ex></expan>
<expan>uns<ex>er</ex>m</expan>
<expan>h<ex>er</ex>ren</expan> von Wertheim
                            <expan>botsch<ex>aft</ex></expan> tun und
                            <expan>v<ex>er</ex>suchen</expan>, ob er die sache noch zu
                                <expan>eine<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>gütliche<ex>n</ex></expan> tag gen ewch well
                            <expan>kome<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>lass<ex>en</ex></expan>. Und was uns denn von im zu antwurt wirdt,
                                <expan>well<ex>e</ex>n</expan> wir <expan>ewr<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>weish<ex>eit</ex></expan>
<expan>g<ex>er</ex>n</expan> zu <expan>wiss<ex>en</ex></expan> tun. Denn wo
                        wir <expan>ewr<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>ersamk<ex>eit</ex></expan> lieb <expan>od<ex>er</ex></expan> dienst
                        etc. <expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan>
<expan>f<ex>er</ex>ia</expan> vi<hi rend="sup">a</hi>
<expan>ip<ex>s</ex>a</expan> die <expan>s<ex>an</ex>c<ex>t</ex>i</expan>
                        Francisci.</ab>
